✅ ❌ 🪓 💼 🗑️
effect

If a "Sylphale" monster effect is activated, while this card is on the field or in the GY: You can 1 "Sylphale Zephyrus Thistle" from the GY; send 1 "Sylphale" card from your Deck to the GY, then, if this card is on the field, you can make this card gain or lose original 900 DEF. You can only use this effect of "Sylphale Zephyrus Thistle" once per turn.

➡️
effect
